      "description": "2020 sedan in fair condition. The exterior shows visible scratches and minor dents consistent with regular use. The interior has noticeable wear including some staining and worn surfaces. Mechanically functional, though some maintenance or repairs may be needed. Priced to reflect current condition.",
      "price": 20000.0,
